flowchart TD
    CAP[CAP Theorem] --> C[Consistency\nEvery read gets latest write]
    CAP --> A[Availability\nEvery request gets a response]
    CAP --> P[Partition Tolerance\nSystem works despite network split]

    P --> MustChoose{Network partition occurs\nChoose C or A}

    MustChoose -->|Choose Consistency| CP[CP Systems]
    MustChoose -->|Choose Availability| AP[AP Systems]

    CP --> CPEx1[Zookeeper]
    CP --> CPEx2[HBase]
    CP --> CPEx3[Etcd]
    CP --> CPBehavior[Refuses requests\nif node is out of sync]

    AP --> APEx1[DynamoDB]
    AP --> APEx2[Cassandra]
    AP --> APEx3[CouchDB]
    AP --> APBehavior[Serves stale data\nconverges after partition heals]

    CA[CA - Single node only\nNo partition tolerance] --> CAEx[Traditional\nRelational DB\nno distribution]
